,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a887daa99b6e4ed24a5b57b9fbde1cde5a7fc62a","tid":2499102,"uid":190705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62ad637daea1c0262852d522721647f58ca5c10a","tid":2499102,"uid":106800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"49091e0c822d6a3d99ff44707505b0fec1401f1c","tid":2499102,"uid":190705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"其實係我女朋友咁樣<br />\n我覺得係俾蝨咬多...<br />\n始終舊公屋重要.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"其實係濕疹<br />\n我果件都係咁 食親D味精/塵就會咁<br />\n成日R穿晒"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:01:46.000Z","msg":"咁有冇話要點先好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"少掂水<br />\n唔用清毒搓手液酒精基本上除咗沖涼液最好乜都唔掂<br />\n真係要洗野都要用手套 而且手套唔好有粉果d 最好好手術手套(要冇粉果隻 有d有粉)<br />\n都係搽類固醇藥<br />\n食野要戒口 要知自己食乜會咁 牛 海鮮 味精 呢類野<br />\nbtw 做運動有幫助 但你發緊最好唔好做啦 好返d先做<br />\n唔係又刺激到"},{"pid":"2e22ca927d4226cd01c40c815be4078ebb854f38","tid":2499102,"uid":243498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:53:36.000Z","msg":"試下用physiogel 當藥膏搽<br />\n平d可以用曼秀雷敦AD軟膏<br />\n<br />\n我以前搽類固醇搽到皮膚好紅好薄 <br />\n覺得再搽落去唔係辦法 把心一橫停左佢<br />\n宜家好番哂連皮膚都變番正常"},{"pid":"023fc20ee1123eae18c31bca1b034ed8c5d4186a","tid":2499102,"uid":113331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"有冇好介紹搽咩好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係唔r佢就好返？"},{"pid":"90db092edb31d3a469cfcab41b3c343d5732e588","tid":2499102,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0573866b8951bdb38d20e05fba47b17118fa398e","tid":2499102,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"5d92bea187a7f482c8b120da32ae741dae297af6","tid":2499102,"uid":138275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io